<LanguageData>

  <!-- EN: Force Recharge -->
  <VFEMechForceRecharge>强制充电</VFEMechForceRecharge>
  <!-- EN: Order the associated machine to return to this platform for charging, regardless of its current battery level. -->
  <VFEMechForceRechargeDesc>命令相关联的机械体立即返回此基站充电，无论当前剩余电量如何。</VFEMechForceRechargeDesc>
  <!-- EN: Attach Turret -->
  <VFEMechAttachTurret>装载炮台</VFEMechAttachTurret>
  <!-- EN: Construct a turret atop this mobile platform. This will require a colonist to deliver resources equal to that turret's normal construction cost. -->
  <VFEMechAttachTurretDesc>在此移动炮台上装载新的炮塔。需要殖民者搬运等于该炮塔标准造价的资源。</VFEMechAttachTurretDesc>
  <!-- EN: Machine destroyed -->
  <VFEMechMachineDied>机械体被摧毁</VFEMechMachineDied>
  <!-- EN: One of your machines has been destroyed! You can dismantle its remains at a machining table. In order to construct a replacement, one of your colonists will need to deliver the following parts to its platform:\n\n{0} -->
  <VFEMechMachineDiedDesc>你的一个机械体被摧毁了！你可以在机械加工台拆解它的残骸。如果想要重建它，殖民者需要搬运以下材料：\n\n{0}</VFEMechMachineDiedDesc>
  <!-- EN: Not enough resources -->
  <VFEMechNoResources>资源不足</VFEMechNoResources>
  <!-- EN: No active mobile turret -->
  <VFEMechNoTurret>没有运行中的移动炮台</VFEMechNoTurret>
  <!-- EN: Needed to rebuild machine: -->
  <VFEMechReconstruct>重建机械体需要：</VFEMechReconstruct>
  <!-- EN: Needed to construct turret: -->
  <VFEMechTurretResources>建造炮塔需要：</VFEMechTurretResources>
  <!-- EN: Reduce range -->
  <VFEMechLowerRange>减少距离</VFEMechLowerRange>
  <!-- EN: Reduce the number of tiles this machine will travel. -->
  <VFEMechLowerRangeDesc>减少此机械体的移动距离。</VFEMechLowerRangeDesc>
  <!-- EN: Increase range -->
  <VFEMechRaiseRange>增加距离</VFEMechRaiseRange>
  <!-- EN: Increase the number of tiles this machine will travel. -->
  <VFEMechRaiseRangeDesc>增加此机械体的移动距离。</VFEMechRaiseRangeDesc>
  <!-- EN: Stop machine -->
  <VFEMechStopMachine>中止任务</VFEMechStopMachine>
  <!-- EN: Stop this machine's progress and force it to return to base. -->
  <VFEMechStopMachineDesc>中止此机械体的任务并强制其返回基站。</VFEMechStopMachineDesc>
  <!-- EN: Start machine -->
  <VFEMechStartMachine>开始运行</VFEMechStartMachine>
  <!-- EN: Start this machine. -->
  <VFEMechStartMachineDesc>让此机械体开始运行。</VFEMechStartMachineDesc>
  <!-- EN: Machine has run into an obstacle! -->
  <VFEMechMachineHitObstacle>机械体遇到了障碍物！</VFEMechMachineHitObstacle>
  <!-- EN: Set area -->
  <VFEMechSetArea>设置区域</VFEMechSetArea>
  <!-- EN: Set the allowed area for all of this platform's associated machines. -->
  <VFEMechSetAreaDesc>设置此基站相关联机械体的活动区。</VFEMechSetAreaDesc>
  <!-- EN: This droid is rideable. People in a caravan will ride the fastest available animals/droids, improving the speed of the caravan as a whole. -->
  <VFEMRideableMachineTip>这种机械体是可以骑乘的。远行队中的人将骑着最快的可用机械体，提高整个远行队的速度。</VFEMRideableMachineTip>
	<!-- EN: {MACHINE_nameDef} ran out of power, and was left behind. -->
